title: #LiveOutside BK Episode 9: Party in Brooklyn, USA
description:
Time to kick back and have some fun. The final drops of paint are on the wall and the party in Brooklyn is starting--with a live performance from Rubblebucket. 

Music: "My Life"-- Rubblebucket
